## Third-Party Licenses

This project uses the following third-party libraries:

### FFmpeg
- License: LGPL 2.1+ / GPL 2+ (depending on build configuration)
- Website: https://ffmpeg.org/legal.html
- Used for: Video processing and compression

### Instaloader
- License: MIT License
- Repository: https://github.com/instaloader/instaloader
- Used for: Instagram content downloading

### aiogram
- License: MIT License
- Repository: https://github.com/aiogram/aiogram
- Used for: Telegram Bot API framework

### pymongo
- License: Apache License 2.0
- Repository: https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-python-driver
- Used for: MongoDB database operations

### python-dotenv
- License: BSD 3-Clause License
- Repository: https://github.com/theskumar/python-dotenv
- Used for: Environment variable management

