- Repository: https://github.com/aio-libs/aiohttp
- Used for: Asynchronous HTTP client/server

### requests
- License: Apache License 2.0
- Repository: https://github.com/psf/requests
- Used for: HTTP requests

### stripe
- License: MIT License
- Repository: https://github.com/stripe/stripe-python
- Used for: Payment processing

### opencv-python
- License: MIT License
- Repository: https://github.com/opencv/opencv-python
- Used for: Video analysis and processing

### psutil
- License: BSD 3-Clause License
